                    <h3 class="ons-u-mt-l">Strictly necessary cookies</h3>
                    <p>These essential cookies do things like:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>remember the notifications you&#39;ve seen so we do not show them to you again</li>
                        <li>remember your progress through a form (for example, an ONS study)</li>
